com.sun.identity.authentication.service

Class PagePropertiesCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.authentication.service.PagePropertiesCallback
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Callback
    Deprecated. 
    This class has been deprecated in Access Manager 6.3 and will not be available in the next Access Manager release. Use com.sun.identity.authentication.spi.PagePropertiesCallback instead of this class.

    public class PagePropertiesCallback
extends Object
implements Callback
    This PagePropertiesCallback class implements Callback and used for exchanging all UI related attributes information such as template name, errorState to indicate whether a template is an error page, page header, image name , page timeout value, name of module.
